#### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///c:/ADAM/smart_attendance_system/backend/prisma/schema.prisma)

**Enum baru:**
```prisma
enum PayrollStatus {
  DRAFT
  PROCESSING
  COMPLETED
  CANCELLED
}

enum EmploymentType {
  TETAP       // Karyawan Tetap (PKWTT)
  KONTRAK     // Karyawan Kontrak (PKWT)
