### Backend — Payroll Controller

#### [NEW] [payrollController.js](file:///c:/ADAM/smart_attendance_system/backend/src/controllers/payrollController.js)

Menangani proses generate dan manage payroll bulanan:

| Endpoint | Method | Deskripsi |
|----------|--------|-----------|
| `/api/payroll` | GET | List semua payroll periods |
| `/api/payroll/:id` | GET | Get payroll detail (with all employee details) |
| `/api/payroll/generate` | POST | Generate payroll untuk bulan tertentu |
| `/api/payroll/:id/finalize` | PUT | Finalize payroll (lock) |
| `/api/payroll/:id/cancel` | PUT | Cancel payroll |
| `/api/payroll/:id/export-excel` | GET | Export payroll ke Excel |
| `/api/payroll/:id/export-pdf` | GET | Export payroll ke PDF |
| `/api/payroll/:id/slip/:empId` | GET | Generate slip gaji individual |

**Logika Generate Payroll:**

```
1. Ambil semua karyawan ACTIVE dengan EmployeeSalary
2. Untuk setiap karyawan:
   a. Hitung kehadiran bulan tersebut dari tabel Attendance
   b. Hitung gaji pokok:
      - MONTHLY: baseSalary (pro-rata jika ada mangkir/absent)
      - DAILY: dailyRate × daysPresent
   c. Hitung tunjangan dari components (allowance)
   d. Hitung potongan dari components (deduction)
   e. Hitung lembur:
      - Ambil jam kerja > shift endTime per hari
      - Apply overtime rules berdasarkan tier
      - overtimePay = Σ(hours × multiplier × hourlyRate)
   f. grossPay = proRatedSalary + allowances + overtimePay
   g. netPay = grossPay - totalDeductions
3. Simpan ke Payroll + PayrollDetail
```

